name: Metal Gear | Quiet
description:
This LoRA is trained with 111 images, varying from cosplays to fan arts, of Metal Gear's Quiet.

Simply load up your favorite model and use <lora:metalgearsolid-quiet:1> for this lora to take effect!

This LoRA was trained using SD 1.5 and therefore may not work with all models!

For early access and custom LoRA's consider joining my patreon! https://patreon.com/Crazygirlashleyy

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: Increased image dataset from 11 to 63. Changed tagging method for LoRA training.
